          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "IVR routing, call queuing, and quality monitoring give support teams professional tools without a massive budget. Recorded calls help resolve disputes and train new agents effectively.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Startup founders wearing multiple hats:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You need a phone system that sets up fast and scales without headaches. CallHippo lets you start with one number and grow into a full call center as your business expands.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro Tips to Maximize CallHippo",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/callhippo-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "These come from my own testing and conversations with power users. For deeper strategies, check out ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo tips and best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One number per rep keeps things clean.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Shared numbers create confusion about who owns which lead. Dedicated numbers give each agent accountability and make performance tracking crystal clear.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Review analytics weekly.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The dashboard surfaces patterns you'd miss manually—optimal calling windows, talk-to-listen ratios that correlate with closes, and reps who might need extra support. Set a recurring 15-minute review every Monday morning.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use warm transfers, not cold transfers.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Before sending a call to a manager, the agent adds a quick note in the contact record. The manager reads it during the transfer hold. The customer feels heard, not shuffled.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build skill-based routing groups early.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Even with a small team, grouping agents by expertise (enterprise vs. SMB, English vs. Spanish) improves first-call resolution rates immediately.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
