    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/callhippo.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A smiling sales professional wearing a headset at a clean modern desk, laptop screen showing the CallHippo dashboard with call analytics visible. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How long does it take to set up CallHippo?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most teams complete basic setup—account creation, number selection, and team member addition—in 20 to 30 minutes. Full configuration with IVR menus, CRM integrations, and call recording usually fits within an hour. You can start making calls as soon as your numbers activate, which happens instantly for most countries.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does CallHippo work for small teams with fewer than five people?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. CallHippo's Essential plan targets small teams and low call volumes specifically. You get virtual numbers, call recording, basic analytics, and CRM integrations without paying for features designed for large call centers. Many solo founders and three-person sales teams run their entire phone operation through CallHippo.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I keep my existing business phone number when switching to CallHippo?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. CallHippo supports number porting, which means you transfer your current number from your old provider into their system. The process typically takes a few business days depending on your previous carrier. During porting, you can use a new CallHippo number so your business never goes without phone service.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
